1. CREATE AN APP. you can do this [here](<%= new_developer_app_path %>) after you [turn on developer mode](<%= edit_identity_path %>).
2. DO NORMAL OAUTH.
   - send your users to <%= render Components::APIExample.new(url: oauth_authorization_url) %> with the right params
   - get code at your redirect URI
   - exchange code at <%= render Components::APIExample.new(url: oauth_token_url, path_only: true, method: "POST") %> like any other OAuth provider
   - read more at [OAuth Guide](<%= doc_path "oauth-guide" %>) if you need help figuring it out
3. CALL <%= render Components::APIExample.new(url: api_v1_me_url, method: "GET", path_only: true) %> with that bearer token.
   - use the data returned to populate your user profile
   - read more at [API](<%= doc_path "api" %>) if you need help figuring it out